text: This obsoletes IRM 4.22.9, National Research Program (NRP), International Form 1040 NRP Study.

The material in IRM section 4.22.9 is obsolete because the study referenced is complete, and no longer active for NRP operations. If needed, prior guidance information can be found in the IRS repository. Go to http://oldirm.web.irs.gov/ for more information.
IRM 4.22.9, dated 11-04-2011 is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal.
